                                <img t-att-src="'/logo.png?company=%s' % object.event_id.company_id.id" alt="Company Logo" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; height: auto; width: 80px;"/>
                            </t>
                        </div>
                        <div style="flex: 2; text-align: right; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; color: #b90034;">
                            Financial Services Development Council
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <p>Dear <t t-out="object.name"/>,</p>
                        <p>We noticed you couldn't attend the event <strong><t t-out="object.event_id.name"/></strong>.</p>
                        <p>We hope everything is okay. We'd still love your feedback or invite you to upcoming events.</p>
                        <p>In case you missed it, here are some helpful links
                            <li><a t-att-href="object.event_id.one_pager_image_link" target="_blank" class="text-info">One Pager</a></li>
                            <li><a t-att-href="object.event_id.research_paper_link" target="_blank" class="text-info">Research Paper</a></li>
                            <li><a t-att-href="object.event_id.webinar_recording_link" target="_blank" class="text-info">Webinar Recording</a></li>
                        </p>
                        <p>Regards,<br/><t t-out="object.company_id.name"/></p>
                    </div>
                    <div style="text-center border-top: 1px solid #ddd; padding-top: 15px; font-size: 12px; color: #714B67;">
                        <div class="text-center mb-3">
                            <t t-if="object.event_id.company_id.social_linkedin" style="background-color:white !important;">
                                <a t-att-href="object.event_id.company_id.social_linkedin" target="_blank" style="margin: 0 5px;">
                                    <img src="/custom_fsdc/static/src/img/linkedin.png" alt="LinkedIn" width="24" height="24"/>
                                </a>
                            </t>
                            <t t-if="object.event_id.company_id.social_twitter" style="background-color:white !important;">
